  "description": "Chess in Minecraft! No way!",
  "body": "<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4nSorNb.png\" alt=\"Logo\" width=\"467\" height=\"191\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Like my mods? Support my work:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/I3I41Y7V7R\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img style=\"border: 0px; display: inline; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/kofi6.png?v=6\" alt=\"Buy Me a Coffee at ko-fi.com\" width=\"143\" height=\"36\"></a> <a href=\"https://liberapay.com/LazrProductions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img style=\"display: inline; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://liberapay.com/assets/widgets/donate.svg\" alt=\"Donate using Liberapay\" width=\"99\" height=\"36\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p><br>Ever wanted to play chess in Minecraft? Well now you can, and checkers too! This mod adds chess pieces and a chess board to play chess in game! <br><br><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZWz3orc.png\" alt=\"board\" width=\"262\" height=\"139\"><br><br>All pieces are dyable, so you can form up to 17 teams for a chess battle royale! The boards are dyable too, and you can make them fancy with gold!<br><br><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EQTqCVU.png\" alt=\"banner\" width=\"1860\" height=\"131\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>How to use:</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Use a stick to change a the game piece, use any dye to color them. Use gold on a game board block to engrave it. Use black and white dye to color the board.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">You can craft game pieces and game boards with the following recipes,</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J2tT6Gl.png\" alt=\"piece crafting\" width=\"318\" height=\"153\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2cuQGFg.png\" width=\"325\" height=\"154\"></h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br>You are free to use this in your modpack!<br><br></h5>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Feel free to join our discord!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><a href=\"https://discord.gg/pwn35yhwrG\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/899770/description_c1011ba6-e86d-494f-9f3e-420e40e5433e.png\" width=\"144\" height=\"132\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n</center>",
